posting_body: ['Updated Spectacular corner home.', 'Two bedrooms, one bath, on a large 13,000 SF lot.', 'Zoning is (RO) and can be used for office, Professional or Residential.', 'New fresh paint, updated kitchen, new appliances, and updated bathroom.', 'The property has three sheds with electricity; one is used as a laundry room, and the other two as storage.', 'The property is located one block off Federal Hwy and a few minutes from Dania Beach Pier.', "Don't miss this gem.", 'Pet ok w/ Landlord approval.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (650+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
